Great! Since you have a high skill tolerance, we can explore more aggressive investment strategies that may offer higher potential returns. To tailor a strategy that suits you best, could you please provide more details on the following:

1. What are your primary financial goals? (e.g., retirement, buying a home, education, wealth accumulation)
2. What is your investment time horizon? (e.g., short-term, medium-term, long-term)
3. Are there specific asset classes or sectors you are interested in? (e.g., stocks, bonds, real estate, cryptocurrencies)
4. How actively do you want to manage your investments? (e.g., hands-on, hands-off)

Your responses will help me create a personalized investment strategy for you!
